This duvet cover is made from 100% cotton percale which has a crisp, yet delicate feel. Thanks for watching. Make sure to subscribe to the Bed Bath & Beyond YouTube Channel.

transcripts: Exclusively for bed bath and beyond the bourbon dovey cover and accessories by website I have a classic hotel aesthetic. The bourbon duvet cover and pillow shams are 100 percent cotton percale which has a crisp yet delicate feel. Meeting pillow shams are finished with the same hotel frame pattern as the duvet cover resulting in a bed that is luxurious and welcoming. Decorative pillows add the key fashion elements that complete this elegant bed. Accenting this bed suite are. A great pillow with subtle white golden gray stripes that adds color to the bed. A gold satin pillow that nicely contrasts with the white duvet cover. And a golden gray stitched pillow that creates the perfect layer of texture. Add an ideal backdrop to the bed. They have a gray pattern front with a solid reverse back. Cover and accessories are available exclusively online and at select bed bath and beyond stores.
